; Test account.cc: get_depth and get_account lookup functions
; Exercises the 'd' case (depth) and 'a' case (account) in account_t::lookup

2024/01/15 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food:Groceries    $50.00
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/20 Gas Station
    Expenses:Transport    $30.00
    Assets:Checking

test bal --format "%(depth)|%(account)\n" Expenses
1|Expenses
3|Expenses:Food:Groceries
2|Expenses:Transport
0|
end test
